> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.748</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κεφαλὰν ἐπεμάσσατο</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stroked,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">AP</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.730</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></author> </bibl>): metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πυρὸς δ᾽ ἐπεμαίετο τέχνην</foreign>, Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">artem tractavit,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">h.Merc.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">108</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νόῳ ἐ. ἕκαστα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:816\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.816</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense><sense n=\"III\" id=\"n40109.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. later abs., of night, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">come slowly</tr_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">on</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0579.tlg002:121\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">121</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}